<plot>A short documentary that explores love after 80. When Verna met Patrick, she was a 70 year old widow and he was a 73 year old separated Irish man. All it took was a spot dance, a bottle of wine, and one year to bring them together. Eleven years of happiness in eleven minutes.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?384086</url></doc>
